  "signal_description": "The query is performed on the table 'defaultview-124'. It retrieves the count of cases and assigns it to the column 'No. of Cases'. It also calculates the average cycle time by subtracting the last end time of the event 'Create Goods Receipt' from the last end time of the event 'Create FI Invoice'. This average cycle time is assigned to the column 'Avg. Cycle Time'. The column 'PO Purchasing Group Text' is selected as 'Purchasing Group'. The results are grouped by the third column and ordered in descending order based on the first column. The query returns a maximum of 50 rows."
